{{Quote|The fish swam swiftly in the brook,<br />until he met Teebo's hook!|translated=1|Teebo, from "Ode to a Fish"|<ref name="Ewoks 7">[[Ewoks (1985) 7|''Ewoks'' (1985) 7]]</ref>}}
'''"Ode to a Fish"''' was a short poem by [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]] the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]], which he wrote about a [[Fish/Legends|fish]]. He considered it a masterpiece.

